{"tid":1345003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MTR 不合作運動","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:51:09.000Z","uid":267639,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a12405f0267c735253cb8691948c4ba68146d191","tid":1345003,"uid":267639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:07:34.000Z","msg":"建議大家著白衫 不合作運動 做意係諷刺白衫人<br />\n大家有咩行動就自便啦"},{"pid":"32a69da36fab27a69ed8c56735ef0acd5d7a3d74","tid":1345003,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f0bb813678ba6a4c19b51a6ed1d95dbdac5cf7","tid":1345003,"uid":50099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推廣傳 戰場係元朗 <br />\n有用既熱線</span></span></strong> 請廣傳 人民英雄 直線電話比有需要嘅人 因為報警已經無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4841c68377e7916790dd255a704eaa926a4e8382","tid":1345003,"uid":33736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:55.000Z","msg":"聲明，大家千萬要正確使用鐵路，確保安全，以下教程係學術研究。<br />\n<br />\n月台段信號系統，為安全原因，如果有任何人啟動緊急制（月台或列車），會立即切斷月台列車信號，原意係避免發生任何月台事故，而有關機制喺埋站同離站都有<br />\n<br />\n當列車信號被突然中斷，列車要用限速模式行駛，而限速模式需要車務控制中心批准，過程需要時間。而列車要用限速模式行駛一段路先可以重新切回自動模式。<br />\n<br />\n結論：列車入/離站時，停車/開車過程中喺月台段被㩒緊急制，係會剎停架車，而重新開車要經一大堆程序，好煩同好浪費時間，比喺站內開左車門嘅時候㩒緊急制更煩"},{"pid":"d0ad593c38cd104a07571d20c6a486624bd8f851","tid":1345003,"uid":33736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/K3H6u0mZhFLHN6gbdIyfHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FK3H6u0mZhFLHN6gbdIyfHg&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2Fqd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=a2420c40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/K3H6u0mZhFLHN6gbdIyfHg</a>"},{"pid":"245c76fc82e82ff571b6420741105102ba6dcea2","tid":1345003,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"［冇衝突，不互屌］建議開元朗post者提下開30槍，開槍post者提下元朗，順便提下728將軍澳遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344950</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f58558e265d4eed001b4f9c716778d3e3b8754bb","tid":1345003,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"仆街mtr出賣香港人"},{"pid":"ca50180b2b88d1085ec45e2cfbe4fa88e7f4752c","tid":1345003,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dc874b6165ccd46e0b17e521c9ac739e292cc5","tid":1345003,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d8a48db3aed7132f7a79ec9f2c6f280ada20600","tid":1345003,"uid":267639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2f0bb813678ba6a4c19b51a6ed1d95dbdac5cf7","tid":1345003,"uid":50099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:12:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推廣傳 戰場係元朗 <br />\n有用既熱線</span></span></strong> 請廣傳 人民英雄 直線電話比有需要嘅人 因為報警已經無用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:25:41.000Z","msg":"冇問題 我諗住SD完冇人覆就算 點知咁多 多謝"},{"pid":"ad9e69c07d06c3458bdfbbb22282a28b2c865439","tid":1345003,"uid":267639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"245c76fc82e82ff571b6420741105102ba6dcea2","tid":1345003,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"［冇衝突，不互屌］建議開元朗post者提下開30槍，開槍post者提下元朗，順便提下728將軍澳遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih